    type='think',
    think='No mobile tests. That\'s a gap.\n\n### 5. 文档同步 (Docs)\n- `docs/mo
dules/auth.md` is updated with new file paths and state machine. Good.\n- `docs/
modules/INDEX.md` already had auth. Good.\n- `docs/QUALITY_SCORE.md` still says 
